				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$1\;{\text{kW/m}}^{2}$$\end{document} and 25 °C) are shown in Table 1, and the I–V and P–V characteristics for different levels of solar radiation and temperature can be found in [18]. The PV generator system here has 5 strings, each containing 30 PV modules.Table 1
