				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\upsilon$$\end{document}. This is a local nonphysical model and the so-called ultra-local model. It represents an instantaneous identification of the overall dynamics of the controlled system.

